        b. How to Register...
       ﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄﾄ
        
           Registered copies of NetModem are as follows...

               1 Node License - $20
               2 Node License - $25
               8 Node License - $35

           - Registered - NetModem Information...

           Registered copies of NetModem have enhanced features to
           help  improve  the speed of NetModem on your system and
           over the  Internet. It  includes  support for  OutBound
           Telnet as well as incoming.(See "Installing NetFOSSIL")

           - UnRegistered - NetModem Information...

           The UnRegistered copies of  NetModem, while still fast,
           is not  as fast as the  Registered. UnRegistered copies
           also  have a  connection limit of  50, meaning after 50
           Incoming Telnet  connections,  your BBS Window  will be
           closed and you will need to restart it manually.

